description:
Do you consider yourself fairly knowledgeable about the world of art? Do you yearn to be conversant when the topic turns to art? If you answered yes to either question,   Am I an Art Aficionado  is for you. 

Have fun identifying famous pieces of art.  Educate yourself along the way not just to win at the Parker Bros. game Masterpiece Canvass, but also to learn to enjoy great works that were created to produce intense, emotional experiences.

Learn about the artists that changed art and why these changes are heralded as wonderful events in our history.  Spending some time to appreciate the masters will help you understand why they are considered masters.

Am I an Art Aficionado randomly generates tests that require only a few screen taps to complete.  View additional information about famous pieces and their artists. 

Support for the application includes a support website and a public forum for suggestions, questions and answers.
